OL,3,CInfected-blood victims 'distressed and
OL,4,Cpowerless' over compensation scheme
OL,6,FThe probe published a raft of new
OL,7,Fwitness statements on Wednesday, some
OL,8,Fexpressing "distress and feelings of
OL,9,Fpowerlessness" which Sir Brian said
OL,10,F"can neither be denied nor ignored".
OL,12,FCharities and representatives of
OL,13,Fvictims and their families welcomed
OL,14,Fnews of the new report, claiming those
OL,15,Fin the community are "fed up" with the
OL,16,F"patronising approach being adopted".
