OL,3,CInfected-blood victims 'distressed and
OL,4,Cpowerless' over compensation scheme
OL,6,FIn her October Budget Chancellor
OL,7,FRachel Reeves allocated #11.8 billion
OL,8,Fto compensate victims, administered by
OL,9,Fthe Infected Blood Compensation
OL,10,FAuthority (IBCA).
OL,12,FHowever, campaigners and victims have
OL,13,Fsince contacted the inquiry with
OL,14,Fconcerns about the way compensation is
OL,15,Fbeing implemented and how long it is
OL,16,Ftaking.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/15
