OL,3,CInfected-blood victims 'distressed and
OL,4,Cpowerless' over compensation scheme
OL,6,FAnother anonymous witness said
OL,7,F"anxiety levels are rocketing to
OL,8,Flevels people have not experienced
OL,9,Fbefore, people are crying, unable to
OL,10,Ffunction, unable to eat, feel sick,
OL,11,Ffeelings of loss, trauma and being
OL,12,Fretraumatised".
OL,14,FThey added: "Physical wellbeing is
OL,15,Flow, people are at a low ebb, feeling
OL,16,Fthat all the hard work they have done
OL,17,Fcampaigning has been for nothing."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/15
