OL,3,CInfected-blood victims 'distressed and
OL,4,Cpowerless' over compensation scheme
OL,6,FThe Haemophilia Society said there was
OL,7,Fno time to digest the findings before
OL,8,Fthe compensation announcement was
OL,9,Fmade, and there has since been a "lack
OL,10,Fof centralised support for applicants".
OL,12,FSir Brian added: "The distress and
OL,13,Ffeelings of powerlessness expressed in
OL,14,Fmany of these statements can neither
OL,15,Fbe denied nor ignored.
OL,17,F"Our goal at the inquiry is to
OL,18,Fidentify whether there are practical
OL,19,Fmeasures that could be taken or
OL,20,Fchanges made to address the concerns
OL,21,Fthat have been brought to us.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
