OL,3,CInfected-blood victims 'distressed and
OL,4,Cpowerless' over compensation scheme
OL,6,F"Our intention is for this to be a
OL,7,Fconstructive process, and we are
OL,8,Fanxious not to contribute to further
OL,9,Fdelay in individuals receiving
OL,10,Fcompensation."
OL,12,FThe inquiry will publish further
OL,13,Fstatements next month, when it will
OL,14,Falso decide if additional hearings
OL,15,Fwill be held, the timeframe for
OL,16,Fproviding written submissions, and the
OL,17,Fpublication of its further report.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/15
