OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F417A1741964558
OL,3,CInfected-blood victims 'distressed and
OL,4,Cpowerless' over compensation scheme
OL,6,F"It is heartening that he has
OL,7,Fresponded today in line with his
OL,8,Fcommitment last May to keep an eye on
OL,9,Fprogress for the community and to hold
OL,10,Fthe Government to account for its
OL,11,Fresponse to his recommendations for
OL,12,Fcompensation.
OL,14,F"The process so far has caused
OL,15,Fsignificant distress and anxiety to
OL,16,Fmany of the victims and their
OL,17,Ffamilies."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/15
