OL,6,FKate Burt, chief executive of the
OL,7,FHaemophilia Society, said: "It is
OL,8,Fvital that the Infected Blood Inquiry
OL,9,Fcontinues to use its influence and
OL,10,Finsights to keep pressure on
OL,11,Fgovernment to deliver its
OL,12,Frecommendations in the way that was
OL,13,Fintended.
OL,15,F"As a charity on the front line of
OL,16,Fsupport for this community, we see the
OL,17,Fdamaging impact of the anger,
OL,18,Fconfusion and despair caused by
OL,19,Funcertainty over the Government's
OL,20,Fcompensation scheme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/15
