OL,3,CInfected-blood victims 'distressed and
OL,4,Cpowerless' over compensation scheme
OL,6,F"The infected blood community feels
OL,7,Flet down and left out. Some are
OL,8,Fstarting to lose hope that they will
OL,9,Fever receive a fair compensation
OL,10,Fpayment.
OL,12,F"We hope the inquiry's intervention
OL,13,Fwill result in a swift and fair
OL,14,Foutcome for everyone who has suffered
OL,15,Fas a result of this scandal."
OL,17,FA Government spokesperson said: "The
OL,18,Fvictims of this scandal have suffered
OL,19,Funspeakably.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/15
