OL,6,F"We remain fully committed to
OL,7,Fcooperating with the Inquiry and
OL,8,Facting on its recommendations, and are
OL,9,Fgrateful for its comprehensive work to
OL,10,Fdate.
OL,12,F"So far we have set aside #11.8
OL,13,Fbillion to compensate victims of
OL,14,Finfected blood, made compensation
OL,15,Foffers of over #48 million and paid #1
OL,16,Fbillion in interim payments."
